        <item>
            <title>少年 JUMP 玩具展登陆铜锣湾，打卡位 + 会场限定品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/jump2024/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jump2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/jump2024/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:28:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262814</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>铜锣湾时代广场于 2024 年 9 月 13 日正式展开全港首个「JUMP FIGURE CRAFT STUDIO」期间限定展览，展期将持续至 11 月 3 日。这次展览展示了《周刊少年 JUMP》四大经典作品，包括《龙珠》、《火影忍者》、《ONE PIECE》和《SPY×FAMILY 间谍家家酒》，并将漫画角色以 Figure 形式呈现，让参观者从中回顾角色的演变和招式特色。展区内设置了多个场景，让动漫迷可以深入了解角色的背景及故事发展。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《龙珠》展区重现了基洛博士的秘密实验室，观众可以进入胶囊，化身成为人造人拍照留念。展区中展示了多款《龙珠》系列的珍贵 Figure，展现主角孙悟空及其他历代角色的变化，从最早的造型到近期的形象演变，这些 Figure 不仅展现了角色的招式动作，也透过细腻的雕工展示出其鲜明的个性。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在《ONE PIECE》展区，参观者可以乘坐千阳号，透过多个展示的 Figure 了解不同版本的角色造型及发展过程。展区中特别展示了《ONE PIECE》系列 Figure 的材质和细节演变，从初代作品到当今的作品，Figure 的精致度和动感都得到了显著提升，带领观众一同见证角色在动画和漫画中的成长。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《火影忍者》展区则重现了木叶忍者村的标志大门，吸引了大量《火影忍者》粉丝前来打卡。展区内最大的亮点是 3.9 米高的火影岩 3D 场景以及 1 比 1 大小的漩涡鸣人立像，这些精美的展品为观众呈现了角色的标志性招式，包括螺旋丸、仙法熔遁螺旋手里剑等经典场景，并让粉丝们可以近距离感受鸣人等角色的招式魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《SPY×FAMILY 间谍家家酒》展区以东国市镇的大街为主题，展出了安妮亚和她的父亲洛伊德·佛杰的 1:1 立像，这也是洛伊德首次在香港亮相。展区内的设计让参观者犹如置身于动画中的场景，近距离观察安妮亚一家在东国的生活情景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>除了展览部分，TAMASHII NATIONS POP-UP SPOT 快闪店同时在二楼中庭开设，发售超过 300 款商品，其中包括多款 JUMP 系列的独家限定品。而５款会场限量商品将以网上登记抽签的形式发售，粉丝们需透过 Tamashii Nations Hong Kong 的 Facebook 专页查阅具体购买资讯，不过消息指现时已被全数认购售罄了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1230-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1