            <title>微信刷掌支付登陆澳门，境外首站支援 + 用掌纹掌静脉辨识技术</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/wechat-palmpayment-available-in-macau/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-palmpayment-available-in-macau</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/wechat-palmpayment-available-in-macau/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 07:31:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[买物情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[刷掌支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信刷掌]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[澳门]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[澳门银河]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262697</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">微信日前举行发布会正式宣布在微信支付、中国工商银行（澳门）和澳门银河的紧密合作下，将会在澳门银河推出首个境外刷掌支付服务。本次合作项目首阶段会在星际酒店、澳门银河、澳门百老汇和银河综艺馆共 60 多个商铺和服务点率先引入刷掌登记及支付功能，已经开通内地微信钱包支付及刷掌支付的用户即可使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1262740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1262739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1262700 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-694x440.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-694x440.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.tencent.com/index.php/zh-cn/articles/2201934.html">腾讯</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">微信支付硬件创新负责人夏凯在发布会现场介绍刷掌支付的技术原理，以「掌纹 + 掌静脉」的识别技术实现无接触且高准确度的支付体验。目前刷掌支付在境内已经广泛地应用在零售、餐饮、交通等场景，微信支付跨境业务港澳台区域负责人陈张维希望境外地区引入刷掌支付技术能有效帮助境外商家提升经营效率。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_23582"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yCY1MemXzuY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前澳门银河亦就微信刷掌支付的引入而推出了一系列的优惠，中国内地微信支付用户在 9 月 10 日至 10 月 31 日活动期间于银河娱乐集团成员旗下指定商户新开通及使用微信刷掌支付，首单消费可立即扣减高达 88.8 人民币，于指定商户使用微信支付亦可享高达 180 人民币的满减券。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.tencent.com/index.php/zh-cn/articles/2201934.html">腾讯</a>、<a href="https://www.galaxymacau.com/zh-hant/offers/dining/wave-and-pay/">澳门银河</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.galaxymacau.com/zh-hant/offers/dining/wave-and-pay/">澳门银河</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-wechat-2/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传微信拒绝支援 iPhone 16   Apple：正与腾讯协商解决</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/23/smartone-macau-service-ended/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">数码通停止澳门流动通讯服务，现有客户将转至澳门电讯</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/govt-whatsapp-new-rule/software/pc-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新指引限制公务员使用个人通讯软件　需要获部门主管批准才能用 WhatsApp</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/wechat-palmpayment-available-in-macau/life-tech/epayment/">微信刷掌支付登陆澳门，境外首站支援 + 用掌纹掌静脉辨识技术</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
