            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262708</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">一众等待换新机的果迷要密切留意了，Apple 早前全新发布的 iPhone 16 及 iPhone 16 Pro 系列、Apple Watch Series 10 和 AirPods 4 将会在香港时间今晚 8 点起开放接受预订。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1262717 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleiphone16geo_inl-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleiphone16geo_inl-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleiphone16geo_inl.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleiphone16geo_inl-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2024/09/get-ready-to-upgrade-to-the-new-iphone-16-apple-watch-and-airpods-lineups/">Apple</a></p><p>Apple 表示，使用 iPhone 12 或更新型号的 iPhone 换购 iPhone 16 及 iPhone 16 Pro 系列产品时可享 $1300 至 $5400 的以旧换新回赠优惠。</p><p>其他全新推出的产品如 Apple Watch Series 10、全新黑色钛金属 Apple Watch Ultra 2、AirPods 4 以及新配色的 AirPods Max 亦会在今晚 8 点同步开放接受预订，上述产品将随 iPhone 16 及 iPhone 16 Pro 系列一同于 9 月 20 日正式公开发售。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1262713 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleapplewatchultra-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleapplewatchultra-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleapplewatchultra.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleapplewatchultra-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1262712 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleairpods4withact-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleairpods4withact-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleairpods4withact.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/appleairpods4withact-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2024/09/get-ready-to-upgrade-to-the-new-iphone-16-apple-watch-and-airpods-lineups/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2024/09/get-ready-to-upgrade-to-the-new-iphone-16-apple-watch-and-airpods-lineups/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手评测，港人最爱 18 个功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/apple-watch-coolz-app-face/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Apple Watch 过百款表面免费玩　可设定动画表面</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学+实试】Apple Intelligence 7 大实用功能　一键校对英文文法 + TLDR 长文总结 + 录音即时转文字</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/iphone16-preorder-hk/shop_guide/">今晚 8 点开订 iPhone 16 系列、新 Apple Watch、AirPods 4</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
